txt.en: Under-leveled stats are generated if you play in a Skirmish that is set to a level below yours.  All stats are tracked, but under-leveled stats are tracked separately and will not count for tournaments.
Your Skirmish Soldier time is depleted - Soldier dismissed.
You cannot summon your soldier during combat.
This will set your Skirmish traits to rank 1 and refund all Marks or Skirmish Marks spent on them.  Do you wish to proceed?
You were not awarded marks because your level was too high.
You have entered an area restricted to Skirmish Soldiers - Soldier dismissed.
Click on the portrait to summon your soldier.
You were not awarded marks because your level was too low.
You cannot summon your soldier right now.

You must complete the Skirmish tutorial. Visit one of the Skirmish Camps found throughout Middle-earth and speak with a Skirmish Captain to properly train. Skirmish Camps can be found in the following regions: Dunland, Ered Luin, Bree-land, the Shire, the Lone-lands, the North Downs, the Trollshaws, Evendim, Forochel, Angmar, Eregion, Moria, and Lothl√≥rien.

This value indicates the Mark acquisition modifier you will receive by running this skirmish with these settings.  Does not include daily quests.
